115
00:11:29.490 --> 00:11:31.560
<i>Beriwon CEO Sin Hoo Ye</i>

116
00:11:35.680 --> 00:11:38.210
<i>Doctora Yoon So Ah</i>

117
00:11:45.750 --> 00:11:48.040
<i>Encontré a Bi Ryeom.</i>

118
